%section#map
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading The Entropy DAO
        %hr.primary/
        = image_tag 'entropyDappDesc.png', class: "img-responsive wow fadeIn"
        %p.lead Anyone can become a Citizen, all citizens share equal control over where Entropy goes, it's purpose and what the community is aiming for. This is the first dApp controlled vessel and an experimental new model for a charity.
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        = image_tag 'worldmap_1.png', class: "img-responsive wow fadeIn"

        %h2.section-heading Route
        %hr.primary/
        %p.lead Entropy steadily heads West on a schedule directed and voted for by the community, avoiding storm seasons while harnessing the natural trade winds.
        %p.lead The community at large decides the next port of call

%section#services
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading Our Goals
        %hr.primary/
      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
        %p.lead The following objectives define the initial purpose of the project, but as the community grows these may be extended, added to, removed or changed by its Citizens.
        %p.lead Anyone can join our community with not only a say in what we do and where we go, but you can join us as we travel around.
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-anchor.wow.bounceIn.text-primary
          %h3 Sustainability
          %p.text-muted.lead Less Than Zero Energy Impact, Communications & Movement
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead Innovate from Waste Materials in our Onboard Hackspace
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead Re-establish Long Forgotten Trade Routes based on Fairness and Equality
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-lightbulb-o.wow.bounceIn.text-primary{"data-wow-delay" => ".1s", :style => "visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.1s; animation-name: bounceIn;"}
          %h3 Dreaming
          %p.text-muted.lead Explore possibilities created by emergent technology
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead Inspire people to make the changes they can bring to the world - dream big
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead Allow people to experience what’s possible: every citizen has the opportunity to come aboard
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-arrows-alt.wow.bounceIn.text-primary{"data-wow-delay" => ".2s", :style => "visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-name: bounceIn;"}
          %h3 New Paths
          %p.text-muted.lead Experiment with different organisation structures
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead Model DAO - see what’s possible, recyclable for other projects
          %br/
          %p.text-muted.lead 100% Transparency - Decisions, Finances, Collaboration - We believe in transparent organisation
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-chevron-circle-right.wow.bounceIn.text-primary{"data-wow-delay" => ".3s"}
          %h3 Just the Beginning
          %p.text-muted.lead Entropy is part of an emerging fleet, heading under full sail into the unknown of the new word
